snippet.title: DeepKaramelFakes
snippet.description: At this stage of my channel, I've discovered the Reface app and am having so much fun recasting actors and musicians, some using the templates from Reface and some split apart, individually refaced one by one, and stitched back together with audio (referring to scenes I've stitched together myself as OC). Sometimes I use my own likeness as I can cheat a bit here and use the best picture I've ever taken :)
